  "texts": [
    "Approximately 3 weeks after FMT, a short-term post-FMT sample was requested.",
    "Pre-and short-term post-FMT stool samples of rCDI patients and their corresponding donors were collected between May 2016 and March 2021.",
    "Additionally, in February 2021 we approached FMTtreated patients of the cohort with informed consent to contact them for later research purposes (n = 53) for updated clinical information and requested a long-term follow-up (LTFU) stool sample.",
    "Clinical data, including recurrence of CDI after FMT, were recorded for further investigation.",
    "Stool samples were stored at -80 °C until DNA extraction for metagenomics sequencing or stored in an end concentration of 10% glycerol until MDR culture testing."
  ],
